<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3948.1.4>
    dc:creator "Kotharambath, Ramachandran; Wilkinson, Mark; Oommen, Oommen V.; Gower, David J." ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Indian caecilian highlights challenges for species delimitation within Gegeneophis Peters, 1879 (Amphibia: Gymnophiona: Indotyphlidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.242124>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.242125>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.242126> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.242124>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Holotype (BNHS 5420) of Gegeneophis tejaswini sp. nov. Whole body shown in dorsal (A) and ventral (B) views; head, collars and anteriormost two primary annuli shown in dorsal (C), right lateral (D) and ventral (E) views; body terminus shown in dorsal (F), left lateral (G) and ventral (H) views. Scale bar for whole body views 10 mm, for anterior and posterior close-up views 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/242124/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.242125>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Gegeneophis tejaswini sp. nov. in life, two topotypic specimens found approximately 0.5 m apart. The larger specimen (preserved TL = 196 mm) is adult female paratype BNHS 5421." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/242125/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.242126>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Habitat at Bedoor, type locality of Gegeneophis tejaswini sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/242126/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

